<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">开启或关闭蓝牙</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">您可以打开蓝牙以连接其他蓝牙设备，或关闭蓝牙以节省电力。要打开蓝牙：</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览中后输入<span class="gui">蓝牙</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击 <span class="gui">蓝牙</span> 打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">将顶部的开关设置为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<p class="p">许多笔记本电脑都有一个硬件开关或组合键来打开和关闭蓝牙。找找电脑上的开关或键盘上的按键。这个键通常需借助 <span class="key"><kbd class="key-Fn">Fn</kbd></span> 键使用。</p>
<p class="p">要关闭蓝牙：</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">从顶栏右侧打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#systemmenu" title="系统菜单">系统菜单</a></span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">选择 <span class="gui"><span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/bluetooth-active-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt=""></span></span> 蓝牙</span>。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
